title: Sports Person of the Week - Travis Etienne
text:
Sports Person of the Week - Travis Etienne - KPLC 7 News, Lake Charles, Louisiana Member Center: Sports Person of the Week - Travis Etienne Posted: SPORTS PERSON OF THE WEEK (KPLC) JENNINGS, LA (KPLC) - 
Jennings running back Travis Etienne has given opponents fits this season. 
"I like to look at myself as a an all-around running back," said Etienne. I've got a little speed, vision and a little power that I bring to the table." 
Another way to describe Ettine is productive. The running back currently leads all of SWLA with 1,492 yards rushing and 25 touchdowns. Last week vs Iota he had another dominating performance, running for 260 yards an five touchdowns. 
"I've just been running the ball-- that's my job. Everybody on the team has one job. We just do the job to the best of our ability. I have linemen open up holes for me, so I just run behind them. They deserve all the credit." 
Despite only four games remaining in the regular season, the Bulldog back still has a few personal goals to accomplish. 
"Coming into the year, I wanted to get over 2,000 yards. Of course my goal every year is to win a championship. Once we get together and get going and click, we're going to be tough to beat." Can't Find Something?
